    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that isn't as tight as it once was. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading, while the interior shows clear signs of wear on the upholstery. It\u2019s a solid, budget-friendly option for someone looking for a car that gets from A to B, provided they are comfortable with its cosmetic and minor mechanical imperfections.",
