    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been a total gem. It\u2019s been super well-maintained and still has so much life left for your daily commutes or weekend adventures. It runs smooth and looks great\u2014honestly, you\u2019re going to love how it handles! Everything is working just like it should, making it a perfect reliable companion. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
