      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted 2008 Porsche Cayman S. This mid-engine platform is powered by the 3.4L M97 flat-six, featuring a VarioCam Plus system for optimized valve timing across the rev range. The 6-speed manual transaxle provides precise engagement, complemented by a factory-spec short-throw shifter. Recent preventative maintenance includes a high-flow Air-Oil Separator (AOS), water pump replacement, and a low-temperature thermostat to ensure thermal stability. The chassis remains taut with PASM active dampers and upgraded polyurethane bushings to eliminate deflection under lateral load. While the exterior shows minor road rash consistent with 'good' condition, the internals are pristine\u2014verified by a negative bore-scoring scope and clean Blackstone oil reports. A true enthusiast's spec with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Silver sedan. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Recent oil change. Runs well. Title in hand.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
