    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a dream to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily trips. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today without any fuss, this is the one! It's been well-loved and is just waiting for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
